The paper focuses on Simultaneous Localization and Mapping (SLAM) which is a topic related to robotics and computer vision. Therefore, cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.CV (Computer Vision) are the most likely categories. The paper also discusses deep learning and multi-sensor fusion which are related to machine learning (cs.LG) and control systems (cs.SY). Finally, the paper mentions the potential impact of 6G wireless networks on SLAM, which falls under the category of networking and internet architecture (cs.NI).
